INTERNATIONAL PETROLEUM STATISTICS

This (DOE) report presents data on international oil
production, demand, imports, exports, and stocks.  The
report has four sections.  Section 1 contains time
series data on world oil production, oil demand, and
stocks in the Organization for Economic Cooperation and
Development (OECD).  Section 2 presents an oil
supply/demand balance for the world.  Section 3
presents data on oil imports by OECD countries.
Section 4 presents annual time series data on world oil
production, oil stocks, demand, and trade, in OECD
countries.

