Johnson & Johnson
and Cordis Merge

Johnson & Johnson (1 Johnson & Johnson Plaza, New Brunswick, NJ
08933; Tel: 908/524-3535) and Cordis Corp. (14201 N.W. 60th Ave.,
Miami, FL 33457; Tel: 305/824-2821) have agreed to merge, creating
