DEC 28, 1995, METALS WEEK

US secondary aluminum producer Alreco Metals owes $56,495.32 of accrued
vacation pay to terminated employees, not $56.5-mil as stated in the Dec 28
edition of Platt's Metals Week. The other debt figures listed were correct
according to bankruptcy filings.

