PLENTY HAPPENED IN THE WORLD OF METALS

Having started production in October this year, Pingguo Aluminum will be
able to produce only 40,000-45,000mt of alumina in 1995, but the firm is
hoping to boost its alumina output to 100,000-150,000mt in 1996 to cover
its aluminum production demand, a company source said.

