JIANG ZEMIN PLANS TO VISIT N. KOREA IN SPRING+

     BEIJING, DEC. 28 KYODO - CHINESE COMMUNIST PARTY LEADER
JIANG ZEMIN IS PLANNING TO VISIT NORTH KOREA AS EARLY AS NEXT
