IN NOVEMBER.
     CHINA AND NORTH KOREA CONTINUE TO MAINTAIN CONSERVATIVE
COMMUNIST RULE AND HOPE TO CHECK ANY INFLUENCE FROM THE ONGOING WAVE
OF DEMOCRATIC REFORMS CURRENTLY SWEEPING THROUGH EASTERN EUROPE, THE
